# mbedTLS headers/source, used only to (re)build the TLS shim locally via
# csrc/build-shim.sh. NOT part of the library: the shim is precompiled into
# linked-libs/<target>/libtinyhttp_tls.a, so consumers link binaries only.
csrc/mbedtls/

# Committed on purpose (vendored binaries + shim source) — do NOT ignore, and do
# NOT add a blanket *.a rule (it would exclude these):
#   linked-libs/<target>/*.a          (mbedTLS + shim static archives)
#   csrc/tls_shim.{c,h}, csrc/build-shim.sh
